      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 58.8 - 老子 58.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>福兮禍之所伏。孰知其極？</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>- misery lurks beneath it! Who knows what either will come to in the end? Shall we then dispense with correction?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
