      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>人之迷，其日固久。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The delusion of the people (on this point) has indeed subsisted for a long time.</seg>
      </tuv>
